Name:           Refresh
Object:         /d/Terel/cedric/guild/power/refresh
Cost:           101 mana, Components: instrument, songbook.
Casting Time:   5
Skills:         SS_DEX, SS_DIS, SG_READ_MUSIC, SG_VOCAL, SG_INSTRUMENTAL
Resolution:     Result = resolve_task(TASK_ROUTINE, ((SS_DEX+SG_INSTRUMENTAL)/2+
			 (SS_DIS+SG_VOCAL)/2+Guild_Stat*2))
Failure:        Result = -1   the song fails completely;
			  0   the song couldn't be played;
			 1-20 the song succeeds somewhat but with possible 
			      accompanying instrument damage.
			 >20  the song succeeds completely.

Description:    A song to lift the spirits and reduce fatigue.
		Amount of fatigue healed = (10 + Result/10) * Effectiveness 
		modifier.  Effectiveness modifier is a function of the 
		condition of the instrument (or vocal chords) and whether or 
		not the performer is part of a choir.  It is expressed as a 
		percent.  
Duration:       Permanent.
Requirements:   SG_READ_MUSIC > 10
